quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  11,118,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yenyanga, yakhakholele Abandu okhuba omukanda mulala (okhupara bulala). Kholano balatsililila sa okhukabukhana."
  11,119,"Halali balia aba Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yalolela tsimbabaasi, ne khulwatsio yabaloonga. Ne likhuwa lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi liamala okhubura mbu: “Toto bwene ndilitsusia omulilo kwa Jahannam okhula mumajiini nende Abandu boosi halala.”"
  11,120,"Ne khukhukanilanga okhurula mubuli amakhuwa kabarumwa kho khuko khutinyisie omwoyo kukwo, ne mu kano obwatoto bukhwitsile, nende amachelo, nende obwitsulisio khubalia basuubila."
  11,121,"Ne boolela balia abalasuubilanga tawe mbu: “Khole butswa akamukholanga shinga munyala, toto fwesi khukholanga."
  11,122,"Ne linde butswa, toto fwesi khulindanga.”"
  11,123,"Ne nibia Nyasaye bioosi biefisa mwikulu nende mushialo, ne amakhuwa koosi pe kalikalusibwa khuye. Kho, mulaame Ye, mana mwisiche Ye butswa. Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shakandalanga ehale nende akamukholanga tawe."
  12,1,"Alif Lam Raa. Tsino ni tsinyaali tsieshitabu shinoosinjia."
  12,2,"Toto efwe khweshia Ikurani mulwarabu khomunyoole okhumanya."
  12,3,"Efwe khukhukanilanga tsingano tsindayi muno khulwa okhukhufimbulila Ikurani ino. Ne toto wali nolamanyile tawe kano nikashili okhukhuulila."
  12,4,"Olwa Yusufu yaboolela papa wuwe mbu: “Ewe papa wanje, esie endutsi tsing’ining’ini ekhumi nandala, nende eliuba nende omwesi Ebilutsi (mumaloro) bioosi nibinyinamilanga.""